data.description: Charm meets modern comfort with this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence nestled in an established neighborhood with no HOA that feels like home the moment you step inside. Boasting a generous 1/3 acre corner lot, this property provides ample space both indoors and out.Step through the front door and be greeted by the warmth of pristine wood flooring that flows throughout the home, offering a seamless transition from room to room. Entertaining is a delight in the formal living room, where natural light spills through windows framing the serene outdoors. The heart of the home is the large den, a versatile space perfect for relaxing evenings or hosting lively gatherings.Each bedroom is a peaceful retreat, promising restful nights and energizing mornings. The master suite, in particular, is a haven of comfort with its own beautifully appointed bath.  Outside, the expansive backyard awaits your personal touch, whether you envision a vibrant garden, a playful space, or an outdoor entertainer's paradise.  While the home is being sold as is and is in need of some TLC and repairs, it represents a wonderful opportunity for those looking to infuse their personal style into their next home at a bargain price. The roof is under warranty eliminating that concern. Come see it and feel the potential of a place you can truly call home or find the perfect investment.
